data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home in Central Lakeland, just a stone's throw away from Grove Parks shopping center! This two-story home features a beautiful formal living room, an open dining room kitchen combination, plus office/den behind the kitchen all on the first floor. Fresh paint, modern LED lighting for energy efficiency, and newly remodeled landscaping, creating great curb appeal. Stay comfortable year-round with a new AC capacitor. There's even a 10x10 slab ready for a shed (shed not included). The spacious 2-car garage provides ample storage space. The fenced backyard is a tropical paradise with mango and papaya trees, and a fire pit, perfect for enjoying the Florida sunshine. NO HOA. This home is ready for you to move in and start making memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this place your own!
